node.text:
Welcome to our Crumbl summer fair week! Join Brelynn and Gabe from Crumbl HQ unbox this week's pink box, sharing their favorites, and kicking off this week's Crumbl Fair Game. 🎡💕
 
In addition to bringing fair flavored cookies, we will be hosting our own Crumbl Fair Game! Listen closely in this episode for your FIRST hint in our fair game, then stay tuned as we share a new hint each day on one of our social media platforms! 

The platform will switch daily so make sure you are paying close attention, to gather all the clues. Keep an eye out on Friday for where you should submit your final answer! The first FIVE people to put together the clues win a swag bag! Who's ready to CRUMBL?! 😉🍪

It's a chewy Nutella®-stuffed cookie topped with a melty Nutella® drizzle and finished with a sprinkle of sea salt. 🌰

Tag your Nutella®-loving friends! 👇 #TasteWeekly #crumblcookies

@natgeo is running a 6-week-long Shark Fest & we are diving in on the fun! 🌊

August 9-14

🦈 SHARK (SUGAR)
A vanilla sugar cookie base topped with a perfect blue swirl of vanilla frosting and topped with a gummy shark. 

⚪️ MACADAMIA NUT Our original base cookie filled with layers of creamy white chocolate chips and buttery macadamia nuts.

🌈 HAWAII RAINBOW CAKE (NEW)
A warm cake batter base covered with thick rainbow colored coconut cream cheese frosting.

🧂 HAZELNUT SEA SALT
A chewy Nutella®-stuffed cookie topped with a melty Nutella® drizzle and finished with a sprinkle of sea salt. 

🍍 PINEAPPLE WHIP (NEW)
A chilled pineapple sugar cookie with a swirl of thick pineapple-flavored whipped topping.  ✨ If you don't follow us on TikTok, be sure to swim on over for our biggest giveaway yet, coming TOMORROW! ✨  🚨 GIVEAWAY 🚨
Like & tag three friends on this post 👇 for a chance to win a FREE party box! We will announce the winner tomorrow on our story.

#TasteWeekly #CrumblCookies #PinkBox

📲 www.crumbl.com/app
